<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Login Alert</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>We noticed a new login to your account.</p>
    <p><strong>Date and Time:</strong> {{loginTime}}</p>
    <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>

    <p>If this was you, you can ignore this email. If this wasn't you, please
      <a href='{{resetLink}}'>change your password</a>
      immediately to secure your account.</p>

    <p>Thank you,<br />Review It</p>
  </body>
</html>
